data.description: Your private backyard oasis and dream home awaits you on this beautiful home in sough after Loganville High School district. Enjoy Springs and Summers in your own private backyard with BBQs, pool parties, get togethers and so much more. Home is nestled into a cul-de-sac and sits on a large flat lot. The main floor has 3 large bedrooms, and 2 full baths. Home features modern updates in the kitchen and bathrooms. Open concept from the kitchen to the Livingroom. The floor plan flows from one side to the next. Upstairs offers 2 large bedrooms, 1 full bath and a craft room in the middle. Plenty of parking space with this 3 car garage and large driveway. Don't miss out on this one!! Seller has a VA assumable loan with about a 3.5% interest rate.
